disk space it services course support includes 500mb of space for you to store and share syllabi web files course outlines problem sets notes essays etc newsgroup the usenet newsgroup provided by it services is well suited for online discussion and student participation particulary because newsgroup posts are available and relatively easy to access for the entire quarter last modified fri 18 nov 2011 at 17 28 pages about this service overview class web site class email list class disk space class newsgroup actions registration renewal find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages courses stanford edu coursework stanford edu axess stanford edu undergrad stanford edu university web services mailing list service footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
